name: Limited Edition Posters
description:
18x24in posters hand-printed on 80lb Neena Environment tortilla cover stock. All posters are limited edition prints of 100. All prints are numbered and signed by Ian Adams.

All of our prints come unframed. They are mailed in a sturdy postal tube to ensure they reach you in perfect condition. 

Note: As these are handpulled screenprints, each one is slightly different. Because they are unique they may vary a little from the print pictured. Printed by Andy Macdougall
